  "body": "> This should only be used in very rare cases e.g. if you are not 100% sure if something is a bug or asking a question that leads to improving the documentation. For general questions please use [Erigon's discord](https://discord.gg/hQ2dxbNZ).\r\n\r\nDiscord link is expired!\r\n\r\n***\r\n\r\nIs there any download limiter for phases other than snapshot?\r\n\r\nStage n.5/16 (Bodies) is maxing out my 20MB/s bandwidth to the point where it's impossible to `wget` or `apt update` and it's still going to take ~5 days at this rate.\r\n\r\n[trickle](https://linux.die.net/man/1/trickle) doesn't seem to work.\r\n",
